&lt;li&gt;Expert-level After Effects and Cinema 4D; strong compositing and finishing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Portfolio of trailer graphics, title design, logo animation, and streaming promos&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep knowledge of AV finishing pipelines and broadcast/streaming deliverables&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience leading motion graphics teams with strong creative communication&lt;/li&gt;
