&lt;li&gt;Coordinate production tasks and assignments for social-first, short-form, high-volume content, with an emphasis on video, motion graphics, and interactive digital formats.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support outreach with influencers, talent, and social media partners as needed, helping to centralize and organize relevant project information and details.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handle administrative tasks such as scheduling, document preparation, and budget tracking in support of senior producers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
