&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated understanding of social media platforms, digital trends, and best practices for content engagement across platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with video production and editing processes, media asset management, and post-production workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Highly organized with the ability to manage multiple projects in a fast-paced environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communicator with an ability to build collaborative relationships across teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with project management tools (e.g., Asana, Smartsheet) and familiarity with creative software is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
