&lt;li&gt;Exercise discretion and independent judgment in order to prioritize projects and ensure timely completion of deliverables (internal and external) to specification.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Liaise with internal teams and clients for graphics finishing needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate all communications for graphic finishing internally and externally.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with graphics artists and finance team to maintain and ensure accurate and on time work orders in support of billing and prepare daily graphics status updates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Anticipate project conflicts and work with the client, Creative Director, and Editorial Producer to resolve any conflicts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review all work against specifications before submitting. Monitor and maintain a high level of quality control over all assets and ensure all incoming/outgoing finishing graphics are delivered correctly, to requested specifications, and in a timely manner.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track of the status of current projects and requests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain organization of shared files by managing archival stock footage, researching projects and maintaining efficiency of workflow.&lt;/li&gt;
