&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a motivated Junior IT Support Technician to provide day-to-day technical support for employees while leveraging a background in software development to assist with automation, scripting, and troubleshooting business applications. This role is ideal for someone who enjoys both end-user support and solving technical problems through code.&lt;/p&gt;
