&lt;li&gt;Develop Adobe ExtendScript and UXP scripts for Photoshop, Illustrator, After Effects, Premiere Pro, and InDesign.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build automation tools that connect Adobe Creative Cloud apps to internal systems via APIs.&lt;/li&gt;
